Congratulations!
You Have Beaten
The Clock!

- Tap middle gear to get secs
- Hold middle gear to get mins (cost: 60 sec)
- Hold hour tip until it starts flashing to get hours
  (if you have enough minutes)
- Buy upgrades with minutes
- Unlock goodies with hours
- Reach 12 hours to win the game!
